OL,3,CAndy Burnham pledges more powers for
OL,4,CLondon - but who will get control?
OL,6,FLabour's only leadership contender
OL,7,Fpromised more powers for London over
OL,8,Feducation and housing but didn't say
OL,9,Fwhether the mayor or councils would
OL,10,Fget control.
OL,12,FAndy Burnham is on course to become
OL,13,Fprime minister in three weeks' time
OL,14,Fand promised a complete rewiring of
OL,15,FBritain driven by a 'No10 North' based
OL,16,Fin Manchester.
OL,18,FBut there was a pledge for the capital
OL,19,Fso "London can do more for itself," Mr
OL,20,FBurnham said "and remain the world's
OL,21,Fgreatest capital city".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
