OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1782906493
OL,3,CAndy Burnham pledges more powers for
OL,4,CLondon - but who will get control?
OL,6,FProfessor Tony Travers from King's
OL,7,FCollege London said: "In the run up to
OL,8,F2000 the Home Office didn't want to
OL,9,Fgive up power over the police. The
OL,10,Fchallenge Andy Burnham will have is
OL,11,Fhow to get these Whitehall departments
OL,12,Fto stop hoarding power."
OL,14,FIn his first major speech since Sir
OL,15,FKeir Starmer announced he would be
OL,16,Fleaving Downing Street, Mr Burnham
OL,17,Fpledged to pull people together in the
OL,18,F"broadest possible coalition" to
OL,19,Frevive hope across the country.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
