PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1782906493
OL,3,CAndy Burnham pledges more powers for
OL,4,CLondon - but who will get control?
OL,6,FMr Burnham said: "What hope can we
OL,7,Fhave that it will be different this
OL,8,Ftime? That is the question I would be
OL,9,Fasking if I was a voter right now.
OL,11,F"It is the one I want to answer as
OL,12,Fclearly as I can today, and in doing
OL,13,Fso give the new direction the country
OL,14,Fis looking for after 10 years of
OL,15,Fpolitical turbulence since Brexit and
OL,16,F20 years of falling living standards
OL,17,Fsince the 2008 financial crash."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
