OL,3,CAndy Burnham pledges more powers for
OL,4,CLondon - but who will get control?
OL,6,FDrawing inspiration from Germany, he
OL,7,Fsaid No10 North would be "given a
OL,8,Fmission to strive for equivalent
OL,9,Fliving conditions in all parts of
OL,10,FBritain".
OL,12,FThe department would also have three
OL,13,F"clear tasks" of increasing public
OL,14,Fownership of essential utilities such
OL,15,Fas water, energy and housing;
OL,16,Freindustrialisation; and regeneration.
